addCriteria

void addCriteria(String property,
                 String op,
                 Object value)
Criteria can been appended (logical AND) to the query object.

Parameters:
property - name of the field to apply the criteria
op - use QueryOperators to pass the operation to apply in this criteria
value - the right hand side of the operation

setSkipQueryModifier

void setSkipQueryModifier(SkipQueryModifier skip)
Add a skip modifier to the end of the query, which instructs the server to ignore the first 'n' records before returning the remainder.

Parameters:
skip - an object representation of the skip number

setSortQueryModifier

void setSortQueryModifier(SortQueryModifier sort)
Applies a descending/ascending sort to the query result. This is a server-side sort.

Parameters:
sort - an object that represents the descending/ascending sort order

setSkip
